The paper discusses training deep neural networks, specifically recurrent neural networks, using mixed precision on GPU clusters. This topic falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks for classification tasks (cs.NE), which is a common application of deep learning. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of neural networks for image analysis (cs.CV), which is another common application of deep learning. Finally, the paper discusses the use of learning rate schedules to improve convergence, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
